snippet.textDisplay:
It's on like donkey kong..
Shuja Haider and Sahir Ali Bagga , leading season 11.  Shuja has more originality and creatively complex arrangements. Bagga does well with simple yet racy folk tunes.  Both are a treat.  Aima is talented as hell, and very pleasing on the eyes 
I'm a fan of Haider though.
